definition: to flow/to disseminate/to circulate or spread/to move or drift/to degenerate/to banish or send into exile/stream of water or sth resembling one/class, rate or grade

sentences.english: The seepage in riverbank generally induces the bank-collapse so it is one of the key points in the research of this area.
sentences.chinese: 岸坡滲流是江河崩岸的主要誘因和重要研究內容之一。

sentences.english: Chapter 2 is seepage numerical model and boundary condition.
sentences.chinese: 第二章爲滲流數學模型及定解條件。

sentences.english: The unsaturated irrigation supply has duality in yellow soil.
sentences.chinese: 集中的灌溉補給，在黃土層中形成二元非飽和滲流。

sentences.english: Therefore, the study of non-Newtonian power law fluid flow law is important.
sentences.chinese: 因此，研究非牛頓冪律流體的滲流規律具有重要意義。

sentences.english: Research on penetration model of rock is one of the most important subjects in coupled hydro-mechanical research.

sentences.english: The heart of capillary electrophoresis (CE) is electroosmotic flow (EOF).
sentences.chinese: 毛細管電泳的核心就是電滲流。

sentences.english: Seepage exists widely in earth-rockfill dams in water conservancy projects.

sentences.english: According to the feature of the gas permeability, the perforation completion model was bettered.

sentences.english: Seepage flow can be observed in stalactite caves.
sentences.chinese: 在鐘乳石溶洞裏，可以見到滲流現象。

sentences.english: While as for distilled water seepage, aperture increases firstly, and then keeps stable.

sentences.english: Neutrals migrate with the same velocity as the EOF.

sentences.english: This model can be used to analyze the rule of fluid flow near well bore in the elastic-plastic oil reservoir.
sentences.chinese: 該模型可用於研究井眼周圍儲層的變形及滲流規律。

sentences.english: Therefore, the influence of unsteady seepage should be taken into account in the design of retaining wall.
sentences.chinese: 因此，在基坑支護設計中應該考慮非穩定滲流的影響。

sentences.english: Seepage risk is also obvious in dam-break risk except overtopping.
sentences.chinese: 潰壩險情中除漫頂外，滲流險情也較爲突出。

sentences.english: The random permeation model and the numerical answer of soft soil two-layer are established.
sentences.chinese: 提出了軟土二元結構隨機滲流模型及其數值解法。
